/Rebeca_Andrade\"}, {\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}, {\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9949850741500984, \"rank\": 0.0033994041903764173, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"her third gold medal\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vancouver's Shallon Olsen finished eighth with an average score of 13.366.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9998765169274564, \"rank\": 0.00010728457861995817, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shallon_Olsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shallon Olsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shallon_Olsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shallon_Olsen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an average score\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Black said the level of difficulty in her vaults is not quite as high as top competitors like Biles, but said she was happy with her performance and put a positive spin on the result.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Black\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulty\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"her vaults\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"top competitors\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive spin\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The last time I was in an Olympic vault final was in London (in 2012) and I face-planted, so this was definitely a step up from that,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1365, \"end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999977405630548, \"rank\": 1.2420633884870157e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The last time\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"a step\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Black also competed in the women's all-around, where she finished sixth, and helped the Canadian team, including Olsen, to a fifth-place finish in the team event, equalling its best-ever showing.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9682067833101866, \"rank\": 0.032837077498715755, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Black\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's all-around\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"Olsen\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"a fifth-place finish\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"the team event\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"its best-ever showing\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Black described the overall experience in Paris as \\\"pretty amazing,\\\" especially after the pandemic restrictions of the Tokyo 2020 Games.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5844244401201963e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Black\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall experience\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"the pandemic restrictions\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo 2020 Games\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think a lot about this Olympics was really just finding the joy in it, and the gratitude for the opportunity,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympics\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"the joy\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel I tried to soak it up as much as possible and I feel like we had amazing performances for Canada.\\\"\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9600777365701872, \"rank\": 0.034266734254832114, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amazing performances\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olsen, who struggled on the landing of the second vault, said Saturday wasn't the performance she'd been hoping for.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olsen\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"the landing\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"the second vault\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old, who was in her third Olympic vault final, also praised Black, who she said \\\"always has my back.\\\"\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"score\": 0.9669949915210773, \"rank\": 0.03408541864076694, \"text\": \"Black\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my back\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Usually it's just me in the vault final, so its super nice to have another Canadian alongside me, so that was really fun,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2333, \"end\": 2341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9682067833101866, \"rank\": 0.032837077498715755, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vault final\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The night, however, belonged to Biles, who earned her seventh Olympic gold medal in high-flying style.\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2429}, {\"ngram\": \"her seventh Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2472}, {\"ngram\": \"high-flying style\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old averaged 15.300 for her signature Yurchenko double pike and Cheng vaults to claim a second gold on the event eight years after she triumphed in Rio de Janeiro.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2546, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128803714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}, {\"begin\": 2656, \"end\": 2670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2798662224817513e-15, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her signature\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"a second gold\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olsen said she appreciated getting the chance to compete against athletes like Biles, as well as the camaraderie between athletes on the floor.\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olsen\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"the camaraderie\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2785}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2802}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some people treat Olympians like they are not human, especially people like Simone,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2830}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"especially people\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's a crazy athlete but at the end of the day she's still a human.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crazy athlete\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"a human\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's super nice to be out there with her and compete against her because she is one of the greats.\\\"\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the greats\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No Canadian woman has ever won an artistic gymnastics medal.\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3088, \"end\": 3096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9682067833101866, \"rank\": 0.032837077498715755, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an artistic gymnastics medal\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Black appeared on the cusp of achieving the feat on the balance beam in Tokyo, but she injured her ankle while training there.\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3218, \"end\": 3223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999400389803025, \"rank\": 5.99628863728