hape this time, she said.\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"relatively good shape\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for her future, she's taking it day by day.\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her future\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am looking forward to taking a rest,\\\" she said, \\\"but still continuing as long as my body can handle it and I am still finding joy and I have goals I want to achieve.\\\"\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3808, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rest\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3677}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3771}, {\"ngram\": \"goals\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And what about the Los Angeles Olympics in 2028?\", \"from\": 3810, \"to\": 3858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3829, \"end\": 3849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9994673402712964, \"rank\": 0.0005329436064634771, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Never rule anything out,\\\" she said with a grin.\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"a grin\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"-- With files from The Associated Press.\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 3950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3933, \"end\": 3949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999970237930662, \"rank\": 2.9704755272808004e-06, \"text\": \"Associated 